text: Phacellus boryi is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Gory in 1832. It is known from Brazil, French Guiana and Surinam.BioLib.cz - Phacellus boryi. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1832
title: Phacellus boryi
